      <link href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/memory">Claude Code memory — @-import semantics for .aidocs/memory/.</link>
      <link href="https://github.blog/engineering/the-ai-memory-fallacy">GitHub Engineering — opaque agent memory as a review-coverage gap.</link>
